.TH "ZENMAP-NATIVE" "1" "07/11/2026" "Zenmap Native" "Zenmap Reference Guide"
.SH "NAME"
zenmap-native \- native GTK4 front end for Nmap
.SH "SYNOPSIS"
.HP \w'zenmap-native\ 'u
zenmap-native
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
\fBzenmap-native\fR is a native Linux graphical front end for the Nmap Security Scanner.
It is built with GTK 4 and Libadwaita and complements the classic Python/GTK3
\fBzenmap\fR application.
.PP
Configuration and saved scans are stored under
\fI~/.config/zenmap-native/\fR.
.PP
Scans that require raw sockets or other privileged behavior may prompt for
administrator authorization through \fBpkexec\fR.
.SH "FILES"
.TP
\fI~/.config/zenmap-native/settings.json\fR
Application settings.
.TP
\fI~/.config/zenmap-native/saved-scans.json\fR
Saved scan index.
.TP
\fI~/.config/zenmap-native/saved-scans/\fR
Saved scan XML files.
.SH "SEE ALSO"
.BR nmap (1),
.BR zenmap (1)
